<!DOCTYPE html PUBLIC "-//W3C//DTD XHTML 1.0 Transitional//EN" "http://www.w3.org/TR/xhtml1/DTD/xhtml1-transitional.dtd">
<html>
<head>
 <meta http-equiv="Content-Type" content="text/html;charset=UTF-8"/>
 <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="IE=Edge"/>
 <title>淘文宝-AI学习体会|智能思想心得|教育心得|领导讲话|重要文章</title>
 <meta name="keywords" content="淘文宝, 学习体会, 思想心得, 教育心得, 领导讲话, 重要文章" />
 <meta name="description" content="淘文宝, 学习体会, 思想心得, 教育心得, 领导讲话, 重要文章" />
 <link href="favicon.ico" rel="shortcut icon" type="image/x-icon" />
 <link rel="stylesheet" type="text/css" href="/stylesheets/reg.css"/>
</head>
<body>
<div class="container registerBox">
    <div class="row">
        <div class="panel">
            <div class="panel-body">
                <div class="col-sm-12">
                    <div class="right-line clearfix" >
                        <h3>新用户注册</h3>
                        <hr/>
                        <div class="alert alert-success alert-dismissible" role="alert">
						  <button type="button" class="close" data-dismiss="alert" aria-label="Close"><span aria-hidden="true">&times;</span></button>
						  <strong>友情提示：</strong>请您确认是否已有平台账户，如果已有平台账户请直接登录，无需注册，否则您可能无法享受平台提供的某些服务
						</div>
                        <div class="col-sm-10 col-sm-push-1">

                            <form class="form-horizontal" id="registerFrom"  method="post" action="/newuser">
                                <div class="form-group" data-id="userName">
                                    <label for="userName" class="col-sm-2 control-label"><span class="text-danger">* </span>用户名：</label>
                                    <div class="col-sm-9" data-input="userName">
                                        <input type="text" class="form-control"  name="userName" id="userName" placeholder="4-20个字符（字母、数字、下划线,以字母开头）"/>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                                 <input type="hidden" name="userType" id="userType" value="person">
                                <div class="form-group" >
                                    <label for="ucName" class="col-sm-2 control-label"><span class="text-danger">* </span>真实姓名：</label>
                                    <div class="col-sm-9" data-input="ucName">
                                        <input type="text" class="form-control"  name="ucName" id="ucName" placeholder="真实姓名"/>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                                <div class="form-group">
                                    <label for="idcard" class="col-sm-2 control-label"><span class="text-danger">* </span>身份ID：</label>
                                    <div class="col-sm-9">
                                        <input type="text" class="form-control" name="idcard" id="idcard" placeholder="身份ID"/>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                                <div class="form-group">
                                    <label for="phone" class="col-sm-2 control-label">手机号：</label>
                                    <div class="col-sm-9">
                                        <input type="text" class="form-control"  name="phone" id="phone" placeholder="手机号"/>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                                <div class="form-group">
                                    <label for="email" class="col-sm-2 control-label">邮箱：</label>
                                    <div class="col-sm-9">
                                        <input type="email" name="email" id="email" class="form-control" placeholder="提示：建议使用有效的真实邮箱，便于找回密码">
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                                <div  id="location-addr">
                                <div class="form-group">
                                    <label for="schoolCode" class="col-sm-2 control-label"><span class="text-danger">* </span>所在地：</label>
                                    <div class="col-sm-3">
                                       <select class="form-control select_auto province" name="province" id="province">
													<option value="">请选择省</option>
										</select>
                                    </div>
                                    <div class="col-sm-3">
                                       <select class="form-control select_auto city" name="city" id="city">
													<option value="">请选择市</option>
										</select>
                                    </div>
                                    <div class="col-sm-3">
                                       <select class="form-control select_auto county" name="county" id="county">
													<option value="">请选择区</option>
												</select>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                               </div>
                                <div class="form-group">
                                    <label for="schoolCode" class="col-sm-2 control-label"><span class="text-danger">* </span>部门：</label>
                                    <div class="col-sm-9">
                                       <select class="form-control select_self school" name="schoolId" id="schoolId">
												</select>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                                <div class="form-group">
                                    <label for="schoolCode" class="col-sm-2 control-label"><span class="text-danger">* </span>角色：</label>
                                    <div class="col-sm-9">
                                       <select class="form-control" name="userRole" id="userRole" onchange="isStudent()">
									   		<option value="teacher" selected='selected'>科员</option>
									   		<option value="student">主任</option>
									   </select>
                                    </div>
                                </div>

                                <div class="form-group">
                                    <label for="password" class="col-sm-2 control-label"><span class="text-danger">* </span>密码：</label>
                                    <div class="col-sm-7">
                                        <input type="password" name="password" id="password" class="form-control" placeholder="密码(至少6位)">
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                                <div class="form-group">
                                    <label for="passwordAgain" class="col-sm-2 control-label"><span class="text-danger">* </span>确认密码：</label>
                                    <div class="col-sm-7">
                                        <input type="password" class="form-control" name="passwordAgain" id="passwordAgain" placeholder="确认密码">
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                                <div class="form-group" style="text-align:center;">

                                        <button class="btn btn-primary" type="submit"> 注  册 </button>
                               </div>
                            </form>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>

</body>
</html>